description.detailed_html:
Create a base patch that supports Ensure operator.

The Patch template parameter must be a Thrift struct with the following fields:

  • optional T assign

  • bool clear

  • P patchPrior

  • T ensure

  • P patch Where P is the field patch type for the struct type T.
